我問了House Rabbit Society (美國兔子協會)為什麼反轉兔子放在大腿上剪指甲是危險⚠️，原來會令到兔子有很大壓力，可引致心臟病。他們的回應：<br />
<br />
&ldquo;Some people put the rabbit in a towel to subdue them- but be careful because it can stress them out. Flipping them on their back can be dangerous because it&lsquo;s stressful and can give them a heart attack. Can you find someone else to hold the rabbit while you trim the nails? Alternatively, can you find a vet who will help and show you how?&rdquo;
